Deryck Maughan
Sir Deryck C. Maughan is a British businessman and philanthropist. He graduated from King's College London with a BA in 1969, and earned a MS from Stanford Graduate School of Business in 1978, where he was a Harkness Fellow. Wikipedia*
On the C-SPAN Networks:Deryck Maughan has one video in the C-SPAN Video Library; the first appearance was a 1998 Forum.
